#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.182:0.2"
msgid "19. Araññavagga "
msgstr "19. Wilderness Dwellers "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: paṃsukūlikasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.182:0.3"
msgid "182. Cīvarasutta "
msgstr "182. Robes "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.182:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, paṃsukūlikā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants there are these five kinds of people who wear rag robes. "

msgctxt "an5.182:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.182:1.3"
msgid "Mandattā momūhattā paṃsukūliko hoti … pe … idamatthitaṃyeva nissāya paṃsukūliko hoti. "
msgstr "A person may wear rag robes because of stupidity … bad desires … madness … because it is praised by the Buddhas … or for the sake of having few wishes … "

msgctxt "an5.182:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca paṃsukūlikā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the five kinds of people who wear rag robes.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.182:1.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

